German[edit]

Etymology[edit]

an- +‎ klicken

Pronunciation[edit]

  • IPA(key): [ˈanˌklɪkn̩]
  • Hyphenation: an‧kli‧cken

Verb[edit]

anklicken (third-person singular simple present klickt an, past tense klickte an, past participle angeklickt, auxiliary haben)

  1. (transitive) to click on
